If it had struck me dead , or struck me blind , Before this cursed time , this worst of Days

your Wives , your Children , all That's valuable , good , or dear , With ready Hands

For what at any other time would be The dire Effect of Rage and Cruelty , Is Mercy , Tenderness , and Pity
